Cell["\<\
We can rewrite the above quantum circuit using relation between the CNOT and \
CZ gates into the following form\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->957819741,ExpressionUUID->"4438f20a-ed44-4fb7-8421-8f1c5cf2d2fe"],

