Cell["\<\
At this stage, there is no reason why we should prefer the CZ gate to the \
CNOT gate. However, we will see below that the CZ gate is better suited for \
the measurement-based scheme. \
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->594853423,ExpressionUUID->"790b158b-d9d5-4841-8ff0-06bb58c49399"],

Cell["\<\
More importantly, the Hadamard gate followed by the measurement in the \
standard basis on the first qubit can be regarded as a measurement in the \
Pauli X basis. This has been made clearer in the following quantum circuit\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->452657728,ExpressionUUID->"0f32a789-90fa-4cc1-8fce-c1ac9c269e02"],

