Cell["\<\
It is indeed physically achieved by rotating the measurement setup, as \
discussed in the tutorial \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Computational Model of \
Measurement\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote].  In effect, the measurement in the Pauli \
X basis on the first qubit transfers a quantum state to the second qubit.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->280543799,ExpressionUUID->"47193fe4-2cdc-4e62-b804-a8744a2eac3f"],

