Cell["\<\
The first qubit is the control qubit. The input state of the target qubit \
enters the second qubit and comes out on the forth qubit:\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->773916856,ExpressionUUID->"bff750a0-f650-4669-bf7d-683e89e4eaa6"],

