Cell["\<\
Observe how the logical basis states on the first two qubits are transformed \
to the first and forth qubit. The result is not exactly what we expect from \
the CNOT gate since we have not corrected the byproduct operators:\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->1029170413,ExpressionUUID->"5604c90e-2fe9-4d96-bf9d-e752daa86251"],

